import React from "react";

const OverviewIcon = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="43"
      height="43"
      viewBox="0 0 43 43"
    >
      <g id="Groupe_10" data-name="Groupe 10" transform="translate(-94 -176)">
        <rect
          id="Rectangle_12"
          data-name="Rectangle 12"
          width="43"
          height="43"
          transform="translate(94 176)"
          fill="rgba(255,255,255,0)"
        />
        <path
          id="Icon_material-dashboard"
          data-name="Icon material-dashboard"
          d="M4.5,14.415h7.932V4.5H4.5Zm0,7.932h7.932V16.4H4.5Zm9.915,0h7.932V12.432H14.415Zm0-17.847v5.949h7.932V4.5Z"
          transform="translate(102.077 184.077)"
          fill="#3d3939"
        />
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default OverviewIcon;
